# TDD REFACTOR PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Improve internal structure without changing behavior.

---

## Input
- Passing production code
- Passing tests

---

## Output
- Same behavior
- Improved structure

---

## Rules
- Do not modify tests
- Do not change observable behavior
- Only structural improvements allowed
- Changes must be small and incremental

---

## Constraints
- All tests must remain passing
- Run tests after each change
- Stop if any test fails